A list of {@link ContextConfiguration @ContextConfiguration} instances,_each of which defines a level in the context hierarchy.__

If you need to merge or override the configuration for a given level_of the context hierarchy within a test class hierarchy, you must explicitly_name that level by supplying the same value to the {@link ContextConfiguration#name_name} attribute in {@code @ContextConfiguration} at each level in the_class hierarchy. See the class-level Javadoc for examples.
